ws.rocket.config

Interface ConfigModel.ConfigModelBuilder.ReaderFactory<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the configuration bean.
    Enclosing class:
    ConfigModel.ConfigModelBuilder<T>

    public static interface ConfigModel.ConfigModelBuilder.ReaderFactory<T>
    Factory for defining common section readers. This factory is for convenience and is optional.
